Package: dttr2
Title: Dates, Times and DateTimes 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
  person("Joe", "Thorley", email = "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", role = c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7683-4592"))
Description: Simple manipulations and conversions for date (Date), date time (POSIXct) 
    and time (hms) objects.
    As well as functions to get, set, add and subtract time units it includes 
    functions to floor objects, set or adjust time zones and complete sequences. 
    It also provides a timer.
